oai_dc:dc.dc:title: [{Fe-2(CO)(6)(mu(3)-Se)(mu(3)-Te)}(2)Mo(CO)(2)]: A novel mixed-metal, mixed-chalcogenide cluster with an unusual structure
oai_dc:dc.dc:creator: MATHUR, P
SEKAR, P
oai_dc:dc.dc:subject: carbonyl-compounds
chemistry
sulfur
reactivity
disulfides
complexes
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: The room-temperature reaction of [Fe-2(CO)(6)(mu-SeTe)] with two equiv, of [Mo(CO)(5)(thf)] yields the mixed-metal, mixed-chalcogenide cluster [Fe4Mo(CO)(14)(mu(3)-Se-2)(mu(3)-Te)(2)], which has an unusual structure as established by single-crystal X-ray diffraction.
